uiEntry.title: root
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address)
function ShowMenu(name) for i = 0, this:ChildCount() - 1 do local child = UIComponent(this:Find(i)) child:SetVisible(child:Id() == name) end end

uiEntry.title: heading
uiEntry.tooltip: These battles can also be played as multiplayer battles.|| You can access these through the multiplayer menu. || Each battle won here opens a path to the next one. || You are awarded a battle honour for each victory, with higher battle honours for harder difficulty settings. || There are four types of battle honour; iron, bronze, silver and gold. || Once you have finished a battle, you can replay it on a harder difficulty setting to try to achieve the highest honour.

state.title: NewState
state.stateText: The Battle of Arcole was a bold attempt by Napoleon to outflank the Austrian army under General Alvinczy and cut its line of retreat before it could lift the siege of Mantua. The bridge crossing the Alpone was key to the battle and where Napoleon was famously seen caring the Tricolour.
